Carrot Foundation — AI Discovery Primitives

This package provides public AI-discovery primitives for the Carrot Network,
including JSON-LD builders, robots.txt helpers, llms.txt generators, and
machine-readable markdown route helpers.

The package is intended for public integration by Carrot-maintained sites and
compatible ecosystem tooling.

You may:

- Use the exported builders to generate AI-friendly metadata and text surfaces
- Link to the package from Carrot-compatible documentation and applications
- Extend your own applications with the package under the Apache License 2.0

